msgctxt "an4.270:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.270:0.2"
msgid "27. Kammapathavagga"
msgstr "27. Ways of Performing Deeds"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.270:0.3"
msgid "270. Samphappalāpasutta"
msgstr "270. Talking Nonsense"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.270:1.1"
msgid "… pe … Attanā ca samphappalāpī hoti, parañca samphappalāpe samādapeti, samphappalāpe ca samanuñño hoti, samphappalāpassa ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—imehi … pe …."
msgstr "… They themselves talk nonsense …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.270:2.1"
msgid "Attanā ca samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti, parañca samphappalāpā veramaṇiyā samādapeti, samphappalāpā veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti, samphappalāpā veramaṇiyā ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—imehi kho, bhikkhave … pe …."
msgstr "… They themselves don’t talk nonsense …"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.270:2.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
